{"_path":"/maps/_devops/rotatelogs","_dir":"_devops","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"rotatelogs","description":"Apache 内置的日志轮转工具，通过管道机制实现按时间或大小切割日志文件。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"简介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"简介"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"rotatelogs-是什么"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"rotatelogs 是什么？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Apache 自带的日志轮转程序。它不独立运行，而是作为管道的接收端——Apache 往管道写日志，rotatelogs 从另一头读，到点就换个新文件接着写。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"管道机制怎么工作"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"管道机制怎么工作？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"配置里写一行 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CustomLog \"|rotatelogs /var/log/access.%Y%m%d.log 86400\" common"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。Apache 启动时，管道符 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"|"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 告诉它：别写文件，启动 rotatelogs 进程，把日志喂给它。rotatelogs 拿到数据后，按你指定的规则（每天、每小时、每 100MB）切分。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"原理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"原理"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"数据流向"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据流向"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{"code":"Apache (写 stdout) → 管道 → rotatelogs (读 stdin) → 文件系统\n"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Apache (写 stdout) → 管道 → rotatelogs (读 stdin) → 文件系统\n"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Apache 只管往标准输出写，不关心后面是谁。rotatelogs 只管从标准输入读，不关心前面是谁。这种解耦让 rotatelogs 可以被任何支持管道的程序使用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"轮转触发"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"轮转触发"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"两种模式：时间间隔（秒数，如 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"86400"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 表示每天）或文件大小（字节数）。时间到了或文件大了，关闭当前文件，打开新文件。文件名支持 strftime 格式，所以 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"/var/log/access.%Y%m%d.log"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 在 2024 年 3 月 15 日会变成 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"/var/log/access.20240315.log"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"消息边界问题"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"消息边界问题"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"问题在哪"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"问题在哪？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"rotatelogs 处理的是字节流，不是消息。它不知道什么是\"一行日志\"，更不知道什么是\"一个 JSON\"。轮转时刻到了，它就切一刀——不管你写到哪。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"举个例子"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"举个例子"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"23:59:59，你的程序开始写一个 10MB 的 JSON。00:00:00，轮转时间到。这个 JSON 的前半截留在昨天的文件，后半截进了今天的文件。两边都不完整，解析时全挂。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"根本原因"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"根本原因"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"管道是字节流。rotatelogs 读到什么写什么，不缓冲、不等待、不理解边界。这不是 bug，是设计如此——简单、高效、不阻塞上游。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"解决方案"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"解决方案"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"应用层保证"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"应用层保证"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"写入端自己负责：每条日志一行，行尾换行符作为边界。大多数日志框架都这么干。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"使用-logrotate"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用 logrotate"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"logrotate 是操作系统层面的工具，它不依赖管道。它的工作方式是：等文件写完，重命名，发信号让程序重新打开文件。这种方式尊重程序内部的缓冲逻辑，不会在半截切断消息。缺点是时间精度不如 rotatelogs——可能差几分钟。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"接受它"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"接受它"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果你的日志格式本身就是行导向的（大多数 Web 服务器日志都是），而每行又足够短（几百字节到几 KB），那这个问题几乎不会遇到。只有当日志行特别大（比如嵌了 base64 图片、大 JSON）时才需要担心。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/rsyslog/rsyslog/issues/409","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Log messages split between files on log rotation · Issue #409"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"与-logrotate-对比"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"与 logrotate 对比"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"table","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"thead","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"特性"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"rotatelogs"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"logrotate"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tbody","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"运行方式"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"常驻进程，实时处理"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"定时任务，批处理"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"时间精度"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"秒级精确"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"分钟级，依赖 cron"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"依赖"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Apache 管道"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"独立程序，信号通知"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"消息边界"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不保证"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"程序配合时可保证"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"压缩"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不支持"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"支持"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://runebook.dev/zh/docs/apache_http_server/programs/rotatelogs","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Apache日志管理精要：rotatelogs vs logrotate"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"配置示例"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"配置示例"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"按天轮转"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"按天轮转"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{"code":"CustomLog \"|rotatelogs /var/log/apache2/access.%Y%m%d.log 86400\" combined\nErrorLog \"|rotatelogs /var/log/apache2/error.%Y%m%d.log 86400\"\n","language":"apache","meta":"","className":"language-apache shiki shiki-themes material-theme-lighter github-light github-dark monokai","style":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":1},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CustomLog \"|rotatelogs /var/log/apache2/access.%Y%m%d.log 86400\" combined\n"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":2},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"chi